</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake new_post['newblogName']
</span><span class='line'>rake new_page['newblogPage']</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>发布本地octopress 到github</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
